You got it. All ready?
Mm-hmm.

110
00:09:48,755 --> 00:09:50,665
Here we go.

111
00:09:50,757 --> 00:09:54,043
Five, four, three, two--

112
00:09:54,219 --> 00:09:57,173
I'm Jill Randall
coming to you live
for Street Copy.

113
00:09:57,264 --> 00:09:59,340
