the violence stop?.

120
00:10:15,532 --> 00:10:18,652
When we stop the men who
put drugs on the streets.

121
00:10:18,744 --> 00:10:22,955
When we stop the men who
put guns in the hands
of children.

122
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:25,827
Then maybe we'll have peace.
Tragic.
Simply tragic.

123
00:10:25,918 --> 00:10:28,325
I'm Jill Randall
for Street Copy--
I abhor violence.

124
00:10:28,420 --> 00:10:30,876
Especially when it doesn't
make me money.

125
00:10:30,964 --> 00:10:34,131
Good night.
Life in the city
isn't cheap.

126
00:10:34,218 --> 00:10:36,127
