that I've been
away too long.

131
00:10:48,482 --> 00:10:50,391
But now I'm back.

132
00:10:51,985 --> 00:10:53,978
Thank you, my dear.

133
00:10:55,155 --> 00:10:57,195
[ Groans ]

134
