00:41:17,561 --> 00:41:21,475
Jill, did you
get my memo?.
The one about
parking in your space?.

527
00:41:21,565 --> 00:41:24,768
[ Chuckles ] No, the one
cancelling the retrospective
on Rollo Latham.

528
00:41:24,860 --> 00:41:26,769
