529
00:41:26,862 --> 00:41:28,819
He's... dead, Jill.

530
00:41:28,906 --> 00:41:30,815
Besides,
this is Street Copy.

531
00:41:30,908 --> 00:41:34,241
Oh.
It's not our kind of news.
It's about sensationalism.

532
00:41:34,328 --> 00:41:36,237
It's about ratings.

533
00:41:36,330 --> 00:41:39,331
Now, you had an assignment.
How come you're not on it?.

534
00:41:39,416 --> 00:41:42,334
