666
00:50:48,674 --> 00:50:51,710
Let's hear it...
for Rhonda!

667
00:50:51,802 --> 00:50:55,218
That's right,
at For Your Eyes Only,
only the finest girls in town.

668
00:50:55,305 --> 00:50:57,594
Guys, come on,
table dance.

669
00:50:57,683 --> 00:51:00,637
** [ Continues ]

670
00:51:59,494 --> 00:52:01,404
Well, hello.
Hello.

671
00:52:01,496 --> 00:52:04,616
I'm looking for someone
that works here;
her name is Laurie.

672
00:52:04,708 --> 00:52:08,753
