01:13:06,303 --> 01:13:08,759
[Honking Continues ]
All right, all right.

938
01:13:08,847 --> 01:13:11,801
Roy, get the doors.
Move it!

939
01:13:30,619 --> 01:13:33,240
What took you so long?.

940
01:13:42,631 --> 01:13:44,956
Some windows
failed my test.

941
01:13:45,050 --> 01:13:48,086
So I made him
do it over.
The windows are acceptable.

942
01:13:48,178 --> 01:13:50,087
What about the rest
of the car?.

943
01:13:52,558 --> 01:13:57,979
Two inches of Kevlar armor
were installed in doors,
roof and hood.

944
01:13:58,063 --> 01:14:01,432
Tires are puncture-proof.

945
01:14:01,525 --> 01:14:06,270
And vehicle is resistant
to all known NATO and
Soviet anti-tank weapons.

946
01:14:06,363 --> 01:14:10,610
And... it has 1 0 CD player
in trunk.

947
01:14:10,701 --> 01:14:13,618
- Hmm!
- So much for Westlake.

948
01:14:13,704 --> 01:14:16,788
The one place
I was vulnerable
is now a fortress.

949
01:14:19,042 --> 01:14:21,616
Boss.

950
01:14:21,712 --> 01:14:24,084
Mr. Perkins,
right on time.

951
01:14:24,173 --> 01:14:28,965
I am always on time, Durant.
That's why I'm rich.

952
01:14:29,052 --> 01:14:32,552
You have my merchandise.
Awaiting
your inspection.

953
01:14:32,639 --> 01:14:35,095
One hundred million,
cash on the barrel.

954
01:14:36,518 --> 01:14:40,101
- Smells wonderful, doesn't it?.
- [Perkins Laughing]

955
01:14:42,816 --> 01:14:46,351
My rifles, Durant.
Ah, Dr. Hathaway.

956
01:14:46,445 --> 01:14:48,484
Would you do the honors?.

957
01:14:48,572 --> 01:14:51,489
[Hathaway]
Now pay attention,
Mr. Perkins!

958
01:14:51,575 --> 01:14:53,947
You simply point and shoot!
[ Gun Beeping ]

959
01:15:08,634 --> 01:15:11,635
- Man!
- [Hathaway] Hallelujah!

960
01:15:13,555 --> 01:15:17,470
* Glory, glory, hallelujah *

961
01:15:17,559 --> 01:15:22,601
* Glory, glory, hallelujah *

962
01:15:22,689 --> 01:15:25,477
* Glory, glory, hallelujah **

963
01:15:25,567 --> 01:15:30,478
** [Hathaway Continues ]
You have revolutionized
the right to bear arms.

964
01:15:33,075 --> 01:15:37,025
In this case,
the far right to bear arms.
[ Laughing]

965
01:15:37,120 --> 01:15:39,030
This calls
for a celebration.

966
01:15:40,123 --> 01:15:42,033
[ Laughing ]

967
01:15:42,125 --> 01:15:46,538
Damn, Durant,
that is one fine weapon.
Thank you, sir.

968
01:15:46,630 --> 01:15:50,046
The boys and I love
a big noise, don't we?.
We sure do, sir.

969
01:15:50,133 --> 01:15:53,051
Let's drink to the green.
Yes.

970
01:15:53,136 --> 01:15:55,806
Mmm.

971
01:15:55,889 --> 01:15:58,261
This gun of yours
seems to work well
on inanimate objects.

972
01:15:58,350 --> 01:16:00,307
But how does it work
on people?

973
01:16:00,394 --> 01:16:04,261
Good question.
Why don't we invite
Miss Brinkman to join us.

974
01:16:04,356 --> 01:16:07,310
I will get her.
No, Roy can get her.

975
01:16:10,779 --> 01:16:13,448
[ Groaning ]

976
01:16:13,532 --> 01:16:15,489
My pills.

977
01:16:17,744 --> 01:16:20,864
Right here, Mr. Durant.

978
01:16:27,671 --> 01:16:30,589
This will save us the cost
of mailing her to Saskatoon.

979
01:16:41,435 --> 01:16:44,056
Let me go!

980
01:16:44,146 --> 01:16:46,933
Thank you for volunteering,
Miss Brinkman.

981
01:16:51,486 --> 01:16:55,650
Ivan, disintegrate
the girl, won't you?.

982
01:17:02,581 --> 01:17:06,661
[ Yells In Pain ]
Robert?.
What's the matter?.

983
01:17:06,752 --> 01:17:10,335
He's having reaction
to his medication!
Take a deep breath.

984
01:17:10,422 --> 01:17:13,340
Let's get him to a hospital.
[ Groaning ]

985
01:17:14,885 --> 01:17:18,005
You're a doctor,
do something!
I'm not that kind of a doctor.

986
01:17:18,096 --> 01:17:20,552
Open doors, quickly!
Yes!

987
01:17:22,017 --> 01:17:24,259
Easy.

988
01:17:37,533 --> 01:17:40,450
One of us is not
who he pretends to be.

989
01:17:50,754 --> 01:17:53,459
Ivan never carries
my pills, Westlake.

990
01:17:56,635 --> 01:17:58,509
[ Speaking Russian ]

991
01:18:00,180 --> 01:18:03,549
Only I am allowed
to wear my face!
[Laurie Gasps]

992
01:18:09,314 --> 01:18:12,232
You are so predictable.
I knew you'd come after me.

993
01:18:12,317 --> 01:18:16,149
All I had to do was dangle
the right bait in front
of what’s left of your nose.

994
01:18:16,238 --> 01:18:18,776
Cuff him and bring him.

995
01:18:21,326 --> 01:18:22,868
Isn't this delightful?.

996
01:18:22,953 --> 01:18:26,404
Two of my favorite people
about to sacrifice themselves
to the greater good.

997
01:18:26,498 --> 01:18:29,997
You're a lovely couple,
but now it's time to play,
"You Bet Your Life."

998
01:18:30,085 --> 01:18:33,834
I would offer some
traditional parting gifts,

999
01:18:33,922 --> 01:18:37,505
but we're fresh out
of cigarettes and blindfolds.

1000
01:18:41,847 --> 01:18:43,970
Dosvidanio.

1001
01:18:51,023 --> 01:18:53,940
Bring me one
of the girl's fingers
and all ten of Westlake's.

1002
01:18:54,026 --> 01:18:57,525
I want to see
the freak suffer.
[ Gun Beeping]

1003
01:19:03,869 --> 01:19:07,487
[ Laughing Maniacally ]
He's a freak! [ Echoing ]

1004
01:19:13,545 --> 01:19:16,083
David.
No!

1005
01:19:16,173 --> 01:19:18,462
Peyton?.

1006
01:19:24,598 --> 01:19:28,927
- Peyton?.
- Durant!

1007
01:19:29,019 --> 01:19:30,846
Peyton, please.

1008
01:19:33,815 --> 01:19:38,193
No, no. No!

1009
01:19:38,278 --> 01:19:40,900
[ Yelling ]

1010
01:19:45,244 --> 01:19:48,743
[Durant ] Jesus!
Get off me, you idiot!

1011
01:19:50,666 --> 01:19:52,243
[ All Grunting ]

1012
01:19:55,003 --> 01:19:57,957
[Laurie ] Peyton!
Laurie, get down!

1013
01:19:58,048 --> 01:20:00,919
Get him!

1014
01:20:00,968 --> 01:20:03,541
[Laurie Grunting]

1015
01:20:05,430 --> 01:20:09,214
Are you okay?. I want you
to get out of here now.
Yeah.

1016
01:20:09,309 --> 01:20:12,974
Grab those guns and that money
and let's blow this pop stand!

1017
01:20:16,733 --> 01:20:20,102
It was you who helped me
with the cab, wasn't it?.

1018
01:20:20,195 --> 01:20:23,481
Yeah. You gotta go now,
Laurie.
No!

1019
01:20:23,574 --> 01:20:25,732
Trust me, go now!
Move!

1020
01:20:50,058 --> 01:20:52,549
Where the hell
are you going?.

1021
01:20:52,644 --> 01:20:55,848
- Perkins, you leave my babies!
- They're my babies now,

1022
01:20:55,939 --> 01:20:58,726
you commie son of a bitch!

1023
01:20:58,817 --> 01:21:00,442
Nazi bastard!

1024
01:21:13,207 --> 01:21:16,955
Nobody walks away from a deal
with Robert G. Durant.

1025
01:21:17,044 --> 01:21:20,247
Where are you,
you spooky son of a bitch?.

1026
01:21:20,339 --> 01:21:22,960
[Durant ] Where is he?

1027
01:21:23,050 --> 01:21:27,379
- Come out, come out,
wherever you are!
- Boss, look!

1028
01:21:40,400 --> 01:21:42,310
You want me?.
Come and get me!

1029
01:21:42,402 --> 01:21:47,645
He's a fucking ghost, man!
Let's make sure of that,
shall we?.

1030
01:21:47,741 --> 01:21:49,698
Well?.

1031
01:21:57,876 --> 01:21:59,785
Eddie, come on!
Wait up!

1032
01:21:59,878 --> 01:22:02,369
Look somewhere else.
You're not gonna find him
behind me.

1033
01:22:06,844 --> 01:22:09,251
Where are you,
you freak?.

1034
01:22:18,522 --> 01:22:21,013
- How 'bout a nightmare?
- [ Gasps ]

1035
01:22:29,032 --> 01:22:30,942
[ Roy] I got him!

1036
01:22:32,327 --> 01:22:34,901
Eddie!

1037
01:22:34,955 --> 01:22:37,576
Eddie,
I got the bastard!

1038
01:22:37,666 --> 01:22:39,706
[ Ivan ]
You got him?
Hold the door!

1039
01:22:39,793 --> 01:22:42,249
You got him.
Good going, Roy!

1040
01:22:44,173 --> 01:22:47,506
Roy?. Uh-oh.
Eddie?

1041
01:22:47,593 --> 01:22:52,420
- You killed my friends.
- [ Nervous Laugh ] I'm sorry.

1042
01:22:52,514 --> 01:22:55,930
- Forgive me?.
- Apology accepted.

1043
01:22:55,976 --> 01:22:58,099
[ Screaming ]

1044
01:22:58,187 --> 01:23:00,678
[ Thud]

1045
01:23:12,868 --> 01:23:15,738
You're next, Durant.
[Laughing]

1046
01:23:15,829 --> 01:23:19,578
Westlake! You're dead!
You're dead, you're dead!
[ Gunshots ]

1047
01:23:27,466 --> 01:23:30,633
I told you,
it's my face!

1048
01:23:51,198 --> 01:23:54,649
Gentlemen, cease and desist
or I'll fry you both.

1049
01:23:55,786 --> 01:23:58,111
Now come down here.

1050
01:24:00,832 --> 01:24:03,750
What I have here
is a 50-50 proposition.

1051
01:24:03,836 --> 01:24:05,793
How to tell?.

1052
01:24:05,879 --> 01:24:10,173
The real Ivan stepped
on a mine in Afghanistan.
He has an artificial hip.

1053
01:24:10,259 --> 01:24:13,509
Mr. Durant,
that's me. I'm Ivan.
I have artificial hip.

1054
01:24:13,595 --> 01:24:17,296
Mr. Durant,
it's me. I'm Ivan.
Shoot him. He's Westlake.

1055
01:24:17,391 --> 01:24:21,258
Shoot him! He's Westlake!
I'm Ivan!
I have artificial hip!

1056
01:24:21,353 --> 01:24:24,271
I'm Ivan!
Mr. Durant, shoot him.
Believe me!

1057
01:24:24,356 --> 01:24:26,265
I have artificial hip.
It's me. I'm Ivan!

1058
01:24:26,358 --> 01:24:29,359
- Shoot him. He's Westlake.
- No, Mr. Durant--

1059
01:24:42,583 --> 01:24:45,156
[Durant ]
Hip, hip, hooray.

1060
01:24:49,173 --> 01:24:53,040
Well, I guess that
narrows down my choices,
doesn't it, Westlake?

1061
01:24:55,804 --> 01:24:57,844
Aren't you
the pretty one?.

1062
01:24:57,931 --> 01:25:01,265
I can't tell you
what an epic pain
in the ass you've been.

1063
01:25:02,352 --> 01:25:04,262
But nothing lasts forever,
pizza face.

1064
01:25:04,354 --> 01:25:06,513
[ Gun Beeping ]
Durant!
Laurie.

1065
01:25:06,607 --> 01:25:09,477
Hmm. A baby doll
with a big gun.

1066
01:25:09,568 --> 01:25:13,268
This must be one of Barbie's
new spring accessories.

1067
01:25:13,363 --> 01:25:16,364
Come to save Prince Charming?.
Take a good look.

1068
01:25:16,450 --> 01:25:20,364
- Put the gun down,
you ridiculous bitch.
- This is for David.

1069
01:25:23,207 --> 01:25:25,911
I got ya,
you bastard!

1070
01:25:26,919 --> 01:25:29,410
You'll pay
for what you've done!

1071
01:25:30,088 --> 01:25:32,247
[ Both Yelling ]

1072
01:25:38,722 --> 01:25:41,213
[ Coughing ]

1073
01:25:51,193 --> 01:25:54,360
Game is over, Westlake!

1074
01:25:54,446 --> 01:25:58,111
- [ Laughing ]
- [ Gun Clicks ]

1075
01:25:59,243 --> 01:26:02,113
Batteries not included.
[ Laughing ]

1076
01:26:02,204 --> 01:26:05,158
[ Yelling ] You!

1077
01:26:06,416 --> 01:26:08,789
[ Yells ]

1078
01:26:12,297 --> 01:26:14,788
[ Coughing ]

1079
01:26:17,010 --> 01:26:19,928
Come here, come here!

1080
01:26:20,013 --> 01:26:23,596
Westlake, stay wherever
the hell you are...

1081
01:26:23,684 --> 01:26:26,887
or you’ll be wearing
her last thought.

1082
01:26:29,815 --> 01:26:32,270
Get in!
[ Screams ]

1083
01:26:41,660 --> 01:26:45,740
- [ Machine Beeping ]
- Hey!

1084
01:26:45,831 --> 01:26:47,823
Run, Laurie,
get away from the car!

1085
01:26:56,466 --> 01:27:00,298
- Westlake!
- [ Laughing ]

1086
01:27:01,930 --> 01:27:03,341
Ohh!

1087
01:27:23,744 --> 01:27:25,701
[ Electronic Squeaking ]

1088
01:27:28,749 --> 01:27:31,536
[ Squeaking Continues ]

1089
01:27:31,627 --> 01:27:35,245
[Darkman ]
Be careful now, he bites.

1090
01:27:35,339 --> 01:27:40,166
You son of a bitch!

1091
01:27:55,526 --> 01:27:59,060
This time, it's forever.

1092
01:28:09,456 --> 01:28:14,035
David's dreams
died with him.
Durant stole mine.

1093
01:28:15,921 --> 01:28:18,127
Protect your dreams,
Laurie.

1094
01:28:20,175 --> 01:28:22,084
Peyton.

1095
01:28:26,181 --> 01:28:28,090
Thank you, Peyton.

1096
01:28:37,651 --> 01:28:41,518
[ Woman On TV] We'll be
bringing you more details
as they become available.

1097
01:28:41,613 --> 01:28:46,109
However, on a sadder note,
today, former anchor
Jill Randall was buried.

1098
01:28:46,201 --> 01:28:49,286
Known as one of television's
most aggressive reporters,

1099
01:28:49,371 --> 01:28:51,613
Randall never compromised
her integrity.

1100
01:28:51,707 --> 01:28:54,376
In fact, the very night
she was killed,
she broke a major story--

1101
01:28:54,459 --> 01:28:58,671
that of the return to power
of crime boss Robert G. Durant.

1102
01:28:58,755 --> 01:29:01,163
Police sources are saying
Durant may have been
responsible...

1103
01:29:01,258 --> 01:29:03,630
for the car bomb that
took Randall's life.

1104
01:29:03,719 --> 01:29:08,048
Whatever the facts, let it
be said that Jill Randall
died as she lived--

1105
01:29:08,140 --> 01:29:11,094
in relentless pursuit
of the truth.

1106
01:29:18,108 --> 01:29:21,144
[ Darkman ] Vengeance
has many casualties:

1107
01:29:21,236 --> 01:29:24,985
the guilty
and the innocent.

1108
01:29:25,073 --> 01:29:29,285
My salvation was buried
with those who would
rescue me from revenge.

1109
01:29:29,369 --> 01:29:32,869
And so, I continue
to face the darkness...

1110
01:29:32,956 --> 01:29:34,865
alone.

